快，快
Hopp, hopp! Schneller!
Hopp, Schneller!

1180
01:21:14,110 --> 01:21:15,360
滚开
Verpiss dich, Mann!

1181
01:21:16,985 --> 01:21:17,902
小杂种
Du Bastard!

1182
01:21:33,235 --> 01:21:34,110
准备好了吗？
Okay?

1183
01:21:36,485 --> 01:21:39,652
阻止“浪潮”
